- Pregnancy dump! 💗 still in awe from the totality of this whole thing… the day we found out I was pregnant, the decision was 100% up to my man.. I wanted him to be in control of when we had our first kid. It’s one thing to be having another child, but when you have a child with a man who actually is excited and committed to being there every step of the way makes the experience 1000x greater.. from never missing any doctors appointments, running to the store at any time of day/night to get me a pickle or whatever I’m craving, daily talks, kisses and prayers over the belly, oiling me down, even shaving for me 🤭.. it’s me turning on movies just to fall asleep in ur arms before the movie even starts (u hate that 😭) to just simply being there for me Thru every emotion… holding & babying me just because u know ima start whining… & you know when I start….. goodluck! 🤭 Lol you haven’t missed a beat and I haven’t went Thru anything alone in this pregnancy.. it’s the little things for me! My first experience was nothing like this… You don’t let NOBODY play with me & I love that for me.. I cannot thank you enough!! You’re going to be the absolute BEST father.. we’ve been keeping these special moments to ourselves.. kept it private and popped out pregnant.. 🫶🏽🤍🐻 Another one, THANK YOU 🤰🏽👨‍👩‍👧‍👧💗🤭🥰🔐
